# Python CLI · argparse

- `--help`: one-line title, `功能特性:` bullet list (3–6 items), then options table — no long `epilog`.
- Define `ShortHelpFormatter` inline (stdlib only); no shared formatter modules.
- Place formatter class immediately above `main()` or `parse_args()` — never between imports.
- `ArgumentParser(..., formatter_class=ShortHelpFormatter)`.
- `add_argument` help: prefix `[必选]` or `[可选]`; defaults via formatter, not duplicated in help text.
- Script runnable as `python path/to/script.py`; no extra repo imports for help formatting only.
